'''''Shooting Star''''' was a [[Corona-class frigate|''Corona''-class frigate]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]].

She crashed with the [[Endor (Corona-class frigate)|''Endor'']] after a mistimed [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] jump, killing all onboard of both vessels.

